{"tid":1657991,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung 申請咗一項「反M字額」嘅專利","createTime":"2019-10-16T10:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T10:49:22.000Z","uid":1886,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7606c54f8965bee96569203e69e6d41f9af10085","tid":1657991,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://businessdigest.io/post/1172/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessdigest.io%2Fpost%2F1172%2F&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=7be6af5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://businessdigest.io/post/1172/</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.apoidea.ai/article/e627b6c3-87fe-4b7c-83bd-f03209078932.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.apoidea.ai%2Farticle%2Fe627b6c3-87fe-4b7c-83bd-f03209078932.jpg&h=3e5197ce&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n眾所鳩知，三星對蘋果iPhone X開始的M字額設計頗不以為然。<br />\n<br />\n今年，三星就申請了一項「反M字額式」的螢幕新專利，設計一反M字額式螢幕，帶來全新風格。三星螢幕設計專利於今年10月7日通過韓國知識產權局（KIPO）的批核。一般的「M字額」設計是在玻璃螢幕上方空出一塊凹槽，再透過邊框整合傳感器，攝像頭等配件。而三星設計的「反M字額式」屏幕則是將玻璃在突出屏幕的頂部，容納手機攝像頭、揚聲器和傳感器。這項設計可保留完整的屏幕顯示面積，讓手機佔有更大的屏幕比例。至於是否確實推出，或是安裝在手機上的表現如何，則有待後續觀察。"},{"pid":"e37c3444183ee14ba53eef586c9bc1105554e76c","tid":1657991,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6c7fa8cb1f59b0ade788a28a7719e3e305d53f9f","tid":1657991,"uid":33325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888f0bd0cda388117bbd4cebd828bcb272d79f95","tid":1657991,"uid":8985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:47:05.000Z","msg":"。。。"},{"pid":"babeb5a2c621e436